<hgroup><h1>A surrogate <em>ℓ</em><sub>0</sub> sparse Cox’s regression with applications to sparse high-dimensional massive sample size time-to-event data</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kawaguchi%20ES"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Eric S Kawaguchi</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Eric S Kawaguchi</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Preventive Medicine, University of Southern California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kawaguchi%20ES"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Eric S Kawaguchi</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Preventive Medicine, University of Southern California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Biomathematics, University of California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Department of Human Genetics, University of California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2,</sup><sup>3</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Liu%20Z"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Zhenqiu Liu</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Zhenqiu Liu</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Department of Public Health Sciences, Penn State Cancer Institute, Hershey, Pennsylvania</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Liu%20Z"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Zhenqiu Liu</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>4</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Li%20G"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Gang Li</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Gang Li</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Preventive Medicine, University of Southern California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Biomathematics, University of California, Los Angeles, California</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Li%20G"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Gang Li</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
